      "suggestion": "Replace callback bags with smaller capability interfaces per workflow (startup init, background services, import workflow, urbit config persistence) and use typed constructors that require mandatory deps at compile time; keep optional behavior behind explicit options structs instead of dozens of nullable function fields.",
